Subject: [PATCH 149/587] FROMLIST: LoongArch: KVM: Add DMSINTC device support

Add device model for DMSINTC interrupt controller, implement basic
create/destroy/set_attr interfaces, and register device model to kvm
device table.

Reviewed-by: Bibo Mao <maobibo@loongson.cn>
Signed-off-by: Song Gao <gaosong@loongson.cn>

Link: https://lore.kernel.org/loongarch/20260409024215.136932-1-gaosong@loongson.cn/
Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
